Gantry::Samples
===========================

These are the Gantry samples.  All the samples are presented together
via a single application.  The individual pages in the application present
different examples, showing how to perform common tasks with Gantry.

There are explanations of the samples in:

    Gantry::Docs::Cookbook.pod

INSTALLATION for the samples is not necessary, chdir into the samples directory
and run the following command

To run this application type:

    > ./app.server

DEPENDENCIES

The samples require a variety of other modules from Gantry and CPAN.
See the source for the sample you are interested in.

